thread.title: William

author: William
title: William
text: I went to my local O Reilly Auto parts store this past Fri.to get an O2 senser for my 03 VW BEETLE. They didn't have it in stock and would have to order,they also told me.that they don't receive shipments on Mondays, so it wouldn't be till wed.i would see the part. I came home,and it's now almost 5:00 p.m.and.i found stockwise auto parts online. I ordered the sender because even with shipping, I paid almost $40.00 dollars less and here it is Mon.afternoon and..My part arrives,2 days earlier than the local store could have got it to me! Thank You!
